---

<section class="bg-via-bg-content" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 md:py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="font-ui text-[1.2rem] leading-[1.9em] tracking-[3.9px] text-via-green">
          - Desde 2011 -
        </h2>

        <h1
          id="hero-heading"
          class="mt-3 font-display italic font-bold text-via-green text-[2.8rem] sm:text-[4rem] lg:text-[6.4rem] leading-none tracking-[0.4px]"
        >
          Asociación de Vida Independiente Andalucía
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-[1.4rem] sm:text-[1.6rem] lg:text-[1.7rem] font-medium text-via-green">
          Ante la situación de atropello al Derecho a la Asistencia Personal en nuestra Comunidad. Vida Independiente Andalucía
          <em>VIAndalucía junto con Asense-A – Asociación de Enfermedades</em>
          <em>Neuromusculares de Andalucía y Trapecistas en la Ciudad</em> nos hemos unido para constituir la
          <br />
          PLATAFORMA POR UNA ASISTENCIA PERSONAL REAL
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://youtu.be/DqvhK780MHc"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex flex-row-reverse items-center gap-[9px] bg-via-green text-white font-accent font-bold text-[1.4rem] capitalize border-2 border-double border-via-green rounded-[16px] px-7 py-3 no-underline hover:bg-white hover:text-via-green transition-colors"
            aria-label="Ver el vídeo"
            tabindex="0"
          >
            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 576 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M549.655 124.083c-6.281-23.65-24.787-42.276-48.284-48.597C458.781 64 288 64 288 64S117.22 64 74.629 75.486c-23.497 6.322-42.003 24.947-48.284 48.597-11.412 42.867-11.412 132.305-11.412 132.305s0 89.438 11.412 132.305c6.281 23.65 24.787 41.5 48.284 47.821C117.22 448 288 448 288 448s170.78 0 213.371-11.486c23.497-6.321 42.003-24.171 48.284-47.821 11.412-42.867 11.412-132.305 11.412-132.305s0-89.438-11.412-132.305zm-317.51 213.508V175.185l142.739 81.205-142.739 81.201z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Ver el vídeo</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-carousel w-full max-w-[1140px] mx-auto" role="region" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-label="Carrusel de imágenes">
        <div class="hero-carousel-frame relative overflow-hidden rounded-[18px] border border-via-divider/60 bg-via-bg-content">
          <img class="hero-carousel-slide" src="/images/pages/recorrido.webp" alt="recorrido" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
          <img class="hero-carousel-slide" src="/images/pages/logos.webp" alt="logos" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <img class="hero-carousel-slide" src="/images/pages/plataforma.webp" alt="plataforma" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <img class="hero-carousel-slide" src="/images/pages/pancartas.webp" alt="pancartas" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-carousel-frame {
    aspect-ratio: 1200 / 550;
  }

  .hero-carousel-slide {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: hero-carousel-fade 20s infinite;
  }

  .hero-carousel-slide:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
  .hero-carousel-slide:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 5s; }
  .hero-carousel-slide:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 10s; }
  .hero-carousel-slide:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 15s; }

  @keyframes hero-carousel-fade {
    0% { opacity: 0; }
    6% { opacity: 1; }
    25% { opacity: 1; }
    31% { opacity: 0; }
    100% { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
